MediaTypeFormatter is an Abstract class from which JsonMediaTypeFormatter and XMLmedia Type formatter class inherit.
1.JsonMediaTypeFormatter
2.XMLMediaTypeFormatter
3.FormurlEncodedMediaTyeformatter
4.JqueryMVCFormMediaType formatter

builder.Services.AddControllers(options =>
{
    options.RespectBrowserAcceptHeader = true;
}).AddXmlSerializerFormatters();
